  "body": "I've build and run besu from source using gradle. then I run `besu --rpc-http-enabled=true --rpc-http-host=127.0.0.1 --rpc-http-port=8888` command and besu run in localhost:8888. \r\n\r\n**I want to add some accounts and send transaction between this accounts. what should I do?**\r\n\r\nI use besu [postman collection] (https://www.postman.com/hyperledger/workspace/hyperledger-besu/collection/11610746-f334929f-c8c3-43ed-bb73-69a6f0d728d8) and I try to use sendRawTransaction method since I get this response:\r\n![image](https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/assets/72091108/59de43d5-1555-44d2-a7e3-a1f21705e7ed)\r\n\r\n@non-fungible-nelson \r\n@garyschulte",
